&lt;li&gt;Lead onboarding, guide integration architecture, and drive deep Buildkite adoption across complex engineering environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct delivery reviews and executive briefings with VP Engineering and CTO-level stakeholders, translating platform findings into strategic business context&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify technical risks, blockers, and expansion opportunities across your portfolio and surface them to the right teams&lt;/li&gt;
