&lt;p&gt;You lead like a founder: you&#39;ll dig into a problem you don&#39;t understand and use it to inform strategy. You have a track record of outsized results from small teams — managing managers, developing staff-level ICs, and owning delivery across multiple product lines at once.&lt;/p&gt;
